UpdateDNS
=========

Edit updatedns.ini to specify the API key for each provider hosting your DNS.
Add a FQDN entry specifying which interface to monitor and update.

	[digital_ocean]
	key       = <api key>
	domain    = domain.tld

	[route53]
	key       = <api key>
	secret    = <secret>
	domain    = example.com
	domain    = test.io

	[sub.domain.tld]
	interface = wan0

	[yep.example.com]
	interface = eth0

	[yep.test.io]
	interface = eth0


